snippet.title: Vanguard: Normandy 1944 - Early Access Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
OUT NOW on Steam Early Access: https://store.steampowered.com/app/941850/Vanguard_Normandy_1944/

Vanguard: Normandy 1944 is a hardcore, tactical WW2 multiplayer shooter developed by Pathfinder Games and powered by CRYENGINE.

Join in the conversation and keep up with the latest news on our Discord channel, forums and other social sites:
Website: https://www.vanguardww2.com
Discord: https://www.discord.gg/jXQKay5
Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/vanguardww2
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/vanguardww2
